  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyber Warrior</strong> is a hacking simulator where you play as an agent of the <strong>Cyber Bureau of Intelligence</strong>, a federal agency responsible for solving virtual crimes. Over the past few months, a group of hackers known as <strong>The Dark Omega Ωrganization</strong> has stolen millions of dollars and now it's your mission to track them down one by one and recover the stolen money:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/ca539e9942b157db0d77511071fbb9a4.webp?t=1762541783\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/ca539e9942b157db0d77511071fbb9a4.poster.webp?t=1762541783\" class=\"bb_img\" width=554 height=291 /></picture></span>                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll navigate the depths of the web, gather crucial clues, interrogate suspects, hack into their systems and do whatever it takes to bring them to justice:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/03cf9a41db73f1f1e4dedd5d22844876.webp?t=1762541783\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/03cf9a41db73f1f1e4dedd5d22844876.poster.webp?t=1762541783\" class=\"bb_img\" width=529 height=300 /></picture></span>                      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay sharp, follow the evidence and trust no one. The deeper you go, the harder it gets to tell right from wrong. Your skills are the only thing standing between order and digital chaos.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyber Warrior</strong> is a hacking simulator where you play as an agent of the <strong>Cyber Bureau of Intelligence</strong>, a federal agency responsible for solving virtual crimes. Over the past few months, a group of hackers known as <strong>The Dark Omega Ωrganization</strong> has stolen millions of dollars and now it's your mission to track them down one by one and recover the stolen money:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/ca539e9942b157db0d77511071fbb9a4.webp?t=1762541783\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/ca539e9942b157db0d77511071fbb9a4.poster.webp?t=1762541783\" class=\"bb_img\" width=554 height=291 /></picture></span>                </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll navigate the depths of the web, gather crucial clues, interrogate suspects, hack into their systems and do whatever it takes to bring them to justice:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/03cf9a41db73f1f1e4dedd5d22844876.webp?t=1762541783\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/726980/extras/03cf9a41db73f1f1e4dedd5d22844876.poster.webp?t=1762541783\" class=\"bb_img\" width=529 height=300 /></picture></span>                      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay sharp, follow the evidence and trust no one. The deeper you go, the harder it gets to tell right from wrong. Your skills are the only thing standing between order and digital chaos.</p>",
